<span style="font-size: medium;">Executive Order Below</span>

<span style="font-size: medium;">WHY? OIL &amp; GAS Ownership-provides 14% for the Nation; 1.8 Million Barrels a day last year. Trump stated, USA efforts in the area. The Area will remain named, the Gulf Of Mexico, on Maps outside of the USA. NOTICE, it does NOT say Gulf Of U.S.A. Our region is the Americas, North, Central and South America!</span>

